Later, Jones took [[Kilgrave]] to the hermetically sealed room in the warehouse, covering its floor with water and making him barefoot, so she could knock him out if he tried to enthrall someone. The video of his childhood played on repeat in the background. Kilgrave, filled with rage, showed dissatisfaction with Jones' betrayal, stating how she tricked him into being a hero, However, Jones stated that he was not, calling him by his real name Kevin, mocking the chosen name "Kilgrave," as well as calling him a murderer. 
